430
00:22:39,420 --> 00:22:43,960
[SPEAKER_02] ali da bi bilo lakše objasniti to,

431
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:45,720
[SPEAKER_02] moram nekako pojednostaviti.

432
00:22:45,799 --> 00:22:49,400
