469
00:24:44,799 --> 00:24:47,480
[SPEAKER_02] I tu je nasto također i patrijarhat,

470
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:51,059
[SPEAKER_02] zato što prije su ljudi bili jednaki.

471
00:24:51,059 --> 00:24:52,619
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, to kad pitaš za jednako,

472
00:24:52,619 --> 00:24:53,019
