473
00:24:53,559 --> 00:24:56,940
[SPEAKER_02] sva lovačka sakupljačka društva su egalitarna.

474
00:24:56,940 --> 00:24:59,420
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, oni nemaju niti klase,

