[SPEAKER_02] u smislu prava i tako dalje.

485
00:25:30,279 --> 00:25:34,539
[SPEAKER_02] I to znači da se

486
00:25:34,539 --> 00:25:38,240
[SPEAKER_02] i muškarci i žene jednako odlučuju

487
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:40,140
[SPEAKER_02] hoće li ići u vezu s nekim,

488
00:25:40,140 --> 00:25:41,759
[SPEAKER_02] hoće li izaći iz veze s nekim.

489
00:25:41,759 --> 00:25:45,460
[SPEAKER_02] Svim odlukama sve donose zajedno.

490
00:25:45,460 --> 00:25:47,500
[SPEAKER_02] Tek kad smo mi prešli na poljoprivredu

491
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:49,180
[SPEAKER_02] se ta ravnoteža poremetila.

492
00:25:49,180 --> 00:25:52,660
