503
00:26:22,539 --> 00:26:24,000
[SPEAKER_02] nije mogla više raditi toliko

504
00:26:24,000 --> 00:26:25,680
[SPEAKER_02] i doprinositi ekonomski.

505
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:29,940
[SPEAKER_02] Tu je muškarac krenuo kao patrijarh nejaka

506
00:26:29,940 --> 00:26:32,640
